text: Phuentsholing United FC was a football club from Phuntsholing, Bhutan,which last played in Bhutan Premier League, the top level of football in Bhutan. The club was founded in 2018. ==References== Category:Football clubs in Bhutan Category:Association football clubs established in 2018 Category:2010s establishments in Bhutan
